"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"       <td>",
"        <p>",
"         Autosomal dominant",
"        </p>",
"        <p>",
"         Defect in mismatch repair gene (MSH2 or MLH1)",
"        </p>",
"       </td>",
"      </tr>",
"     </tbody>",
"    </table>",
"   </div>",
